Author: dreamingsiren
Text: Can you call your insurance company and ask for in network facilities?

Author: cinnamonbicycle
Text: Is out-of-state treatment an option? A couple of my friends from my treatment facility were from Ohio came to that facility severa states away because it was what their insurance would pay for. I haven't heard of many inpatient options at all in Ohio, and the partial hospitalization programs seem haphazardly run at best.
